<p style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; color: #4c4b58; font-weight: 300;"><strong>Add targeted product recommendations to your clients&rsquo; stores with LimeSpot</strong><br /><strong></strong></p>
<p style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; color: #4c4b58; font-weight: 300;">Did you know that incorporating product recommendations into your clients&rsquo; sites can help them get more pageviews per user and up to 40% more traffic and sales? LimeSpot seamlessly integrates with BigCommerce stores to cross-sell and upsell by suggesting products related to each visitor&rsquo;s behavior and 
profile, as well as products that are trending, popular or featured, or have been recently viewed.<br /><strong><a href="https://www.bigcommerce.com/apps/limespot-personalization-product-recommendation/" style="text-decoration: none; color: #4b71fc;" target="_blank">Read More&nbsp;</a></strong><span style="color: #000000;"></span></p>
<p style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; color: #4c4b58; font-weight: 300;"><strong>Incorporate LiveEngage Chat into merchants&rsquo; sites for 20% Off</strong></p>
<p style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; color: #4c4b58; font-weight: 300;">When it comes to ecommerce, the right touch at the right time is critical for building customer relationships and driving business leads.
 LivePerson&rsquo;s chat solution is powered by live data so you can identify high-value customers, or those about to abandon their cart, and engage with them when it matters most -- saving up your precious resources for customers who are really in need.
 On average, LiveEngage users see a 20% increase in conversions and a 35% increase average order value.
 For a limited time, BigCommerce community members can add LiveEngage to their website at 20% off!<br /><strong><a href="https://www.bigcommerce.com/apps/liveperson-livechat-messaging/" style="text-decoration: none; color: #4b71fc;" target="_blank">Get Started</a></strong></p>
